snippet.title: Dragon Hunt Adventure for Playdate Release Tailer
snippet.description:
Dragon Hunt Adventure for Playdate is out now!

Download (for free) this little adventure game set in a classic rpg fantasy world now on tenboe.itch.io/dha

It is available in english and german and in a special children’s version in english and german, too.
